data.description: Beautiful home and a great space for all. Split entry home w/possible dual living! The main level has a living room, dining area, kitchen, and both the master bath & bedroom w/roomy walk-in closet. Separate entry into downstairs to include a family room, full bath, 2 bedrooms and laundry room. W/D hookups are plumbed up and down, ductless heat pump/AC in upper level. Fenced yard, large area for parking/RV, or build a garage. This has a great open feel as well as having separate work spaces.
